Package: maestro
Title: Forest Species Recognition Using MAESTRO Model and IGN Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pierre", "Obsteta", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "pierre.obsteta@example.com")
Description: Automatic recognition of forest tree species from an area of
    interest (AOI) using the MAESTRO model from IGNF (Hugging Face). Downloads
    orthophotos (RGB, IRC) and DTM data from the IGN Geoplateforme via WMS-R,
    combines them into a multi-band image (R, G, B, NIR, DTM), and runs
    inference with a Vision Transformer (ViT/MAE) to classify 13 PureForest
    species.
